{"data":[{"id":562592435,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"ab2b651c629eb54e3ddccea9caef817e","url_token":"mu-shi-han-37","name":"暮湿寒","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3aca97630d87974e8320db41304aaaef_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3aca97630d87974e8320db41304aaaef_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/ab2b651c629eb54e3ddccea9caef817e","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":25,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562592435","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546105255,"updated_time":1546105286,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"comment_count":17,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e所有高赞答案都没有正面回答问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e题主问的是高中生证明哥德巴赫猜想能否保送清北，什么题主证明不出来，清北不是最好的，什么不如当教授等等都不是这个问题的回答，所有高赞答案全都审题不清。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我来正面回答这个问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e首先，我的回答是，不能。至少是不能直接的保送，不管哥德巴赫猜想多难证，你看起来有多牛。这是因为，直接保送这不合“规矩”。据我所知，国家规定的可能有保送资格有省级优秀学生，竞赛集训队，运动员，外国语，烈士子女等。显然，证明哥德巴赫猜想不属于其中任何一类，所以答案是不能保送。如果让你在规矩之外保送，保送制度就乱了套了，比如我救人能不能保送？人命难道没个破猜想重要？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过，规矩是死的，人是活的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果你的实力得到了国家的认可，国家认为有必要争取你这个人才，不让你外流，而你只要上清北。国家可以在规矩限定之内给你最大的上清北的可能。比如你数学好，那就让你参加数学竞赛，大不了提前给你泄题，组织改卷老师认你的字迹，让你轻轻松松进集训队，这样就符合规矩了。或者给你个运动员证明保送，再给你个运动员训练因公受伤的证明堵别人的口也可以符合规矩等等。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e总之，规矩不能破，在规矩之内，可以全力“操作”。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过，不过哥德巴赫猜想再难证，也算是理论数学范畴，这种人国家应该还没有举国争取的欲望，要是应用物理或者工程方向的国家应该会有兴趣得多。当然，清北数学系教授可能会叹服于你的水平，但是单凭教授们也操作不了太多，顶多自主招生你当哑巴交白卷也强行给你降到一本线，你还是得高考。何况现在自招那么透明，稍微被人举报教授就不用做了，我猜教授们顶多加你个好友和你交流交流，在升学方面帮不了你太多。不过有了这些资源，你不读大学混理论数学圈也没问题，大不了破格录取你当讲师，当讲师的规矩一个学校就能操作。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以，答案是不行。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其余的看看高赞答案，清北不是唯一出路，前提是真有人能证明。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"所有高赞答案都没有正面回答问题。题主问的是高中生证明哥德巴赫猜想能否保送清北，什么题主证明不出来，清北不是最好的，什么不如当教授等等都不是这个问题的回答，所有高赞答案全都审题不清。我来正面回答这个问题。首先，我的回答是，不能。至少是不能直…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=1177\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccommen